2. cs.CV (Computer Vision) - The paper mentions the use of visual perception with an Asus Xtion camera for sensing.
3. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) - The paper discusses the importance of reactive control during the final stages of grasping, which could involve AI techniques.
4. cs.LG (Machine Learning) - The paper does not explicitly mention machine learning, but it is possible that some of the algorithms used for grasping and manipulation involve machine learning techniques.
5. cs.SY (Systems and Control) - The paper involves the control of a robotic arm for grasping and manipulation, which falls under the domain of systems and control.
